b(0,0,0);\">Retinol, PHA (Polyhydroxy Acid) , Tremella Mushroom , Blueberry Stem Cells</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Manfaat:</strong> Anti penuaan, kulit lebih halus, mencerahkan</span></p>', 'anti-aging-retinol-smoothing-serum-for-dullness-dryness-skin', 94, '2024-10-15 13:10:12', '2025-01-05 15:00:09');
